title: ArtyTorrent Pack 37-Sony Acid-Either Or Electronica by Twine-WAV
description:
ArtyTorrent Pack 37-Sony Acid-Either Or Electronica by Twine-WAV
----------------------------------------------------------------

This sample CD contains uncompromising electronic sounds that will suit producers making experimental, glitch, or industrial music, or those that just want some weird effects.
If you are looking for sounds like those that appear on hit records, this is NOT the pack for you. Trust me, if you are making any sort of club/dance or commercial music, there is nothing here for you. The samples often sound like "noise" rather than music.

If, however, you want to make slow ambient electronica, then you should get this for the hundreds of rhythmic parts, melodies, pads and effects.
All files are normalized Acidized WAVs at 44.1KHz

More details and mp3 previews at: http://www.sonycreativesoftware.com/loop_libraries/showloop.asp?SPID=298

My next upload should be more useful to the majority of my regular users, so keep checking back.
